message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper deals with semantic image segmentation using convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. However, the application of the proposed method is in medical imaging (cs.MED) and specifically in the segmentation of kidney vessels, which may also fall under the neuroscience (cs.NEURON) sub-category.
